# Tech Stack

This document defines the technology stack used in this project.

## Project Architecture
- Turborepo 2.5+ Monorepo 
- Workspaces:
  - apps/* - Application packages
  - packages/* - Shared packages

## Languages
- TypeScript 5.7+
- Vue 3.5+

## Frameworks & Platforms
- Nuxt 3.15+
- TailwindCSS v4.1+ (with @tailwindcss/vite plugin)
- Directus 19+ (Headless CMS)

## API & Backend
- Directus API
- PostgreSQL Database
- Strapi Integration (v3)
- R2R (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) - RAG/AI search functionality

## Frontend Libraries
- Vue 3.5+
- Vue Router 4.5+
- VueUse 13+ - Collection of Vue Composition Utilities
- Radix Vue 1.9+ - UI Primitives
- Reka UI 2.3+ - Additional UI Components
- shadcn-nuxt 2.2+ - UI Component Collection
- @tanstack/vue-query 5.66+ - Data fetching library
- @tanstack/vue-table 8.21+ - Table components
- tailwind-merge 3.3+ - For handling dynamic class merging
- clsx/class-variance-authority 0.7+ - For conditional styling
- Iconify/Lucide Icons - Icon libraries
- @nuxt/icon 1.10+ - Icon management
- Motion-V 1.2+ - Animation library
- Vue Masonry Wall 5+ - Masonry layout

## Web3 & Blockchain Support
- ethers.js 6.13+
- viem 2.22+
- wagmi 2.16+ (Core) / 0.0.68+ (Vue)
- @reown/appkit 1.6+ - Web3 integration (formerly WalletConnect)
- Solana Web3.js 1.98+ & Wallet Adapter 0.9+
- @openzeppelin/merkle-tree 1.0+ - Merkle tree utilities

## Image Processing & Assets
- @nuxt/image 1.10+
- Sharp 0.33+ - Image processing

## SEO & Meta
- @nuxtjs/seo 3.0+ - SEO utilities
- @nuxt/fonts 0.10+ - Font optimization
- nuxt-og-image 5.0+ - Social media image generation

## Authentication & External Services
- Google Auth Library 9.15+ - Google OAuth
- Google Spreadsheet 4.1+ - Google Sheets integration
- Transform-In SDK 1.0+ - Media transformation

## Build Tools & Development
- Turbo 2.5+
- TypeScript 5.7+
- Node.js 24+
- Yarn 1.22.22 (Package Manager)
- Patch-package 7.0+ - For dependency patching

## Development Tools
- Nuxt MCP 0.1+ - Model Context Protocol integration
- Sass 1.84+ - CSS preprocessing
- Autoprefixer 10.4+ - CSS vendor prefixing

## Development Conventions
- Vue Single File Components (.vue)
- Nuxt Auto-imports
- State Management: Vue Composition API
- CSS Framework: TailwindCSS v4 with custom theme
- Fonts: Custom font provider with Geist and Poppins
- Components: shadcn/ui pattern with Radix Vue primitives
- Icons: @nuxt/icon with custom SVG collections